data.name: LineEndFormat
desc: These values are used to specify which line end format should be used in strings.

items.name: CARRIAGE_RETURN
lines: specifies that line ends are to be represented by a carriage return character (\\\\\r)

items.name: LINE_FEED
lines: specifies that line ends are to be represented by a line feed character (\\\\\n)

items.name: CARRIAGE_RETURN_LINE_FEED
lines: specifies that line ends are to be represented by a line feed character (\\\\\n), followed by a carriage return character (\\\\\r).
